{
  "stem": "22447.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, don't come back for at least a week.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because it has to go to Palestine and come back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It has to go through the censor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we'll see.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I gave her some paper and the pencil.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She wrote a letter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wrote the address on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I looked at the letter, thinking she'd write in German and Polish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, no, she's got it written in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So what the censor saw-- made of it when he looked at it, [LAUGHS] it's written in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, she-- after a week, she came every day, nothing, nothing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one day, I got a reply.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I stood by the door.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I knew she was waiting for it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I saw her in the distance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I waved her this letter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I says. ?] And she, she sprinted like an Olympic athlete the last few yards.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she jumped on me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she hugged me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she kissed me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that was-- what was it I said-- that was a military police's finest moment.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I go to her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I said, what-- I suppose her aunt and uncle were very pleased they heard from her.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And least she got a, an answer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So it did go through the postal service.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She must be about 21, 22.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Channah, but nobody could pronounce it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They actually called her 'Cana,' 'Cana,' 'Chana.' They couldn't pronounce Channah.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Her name was Channah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She came from Poland, actually.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they all disappeared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then one day, I had to escort-- I had to go pick up two Russian prisoners that were accused of looting.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And looting was a serious crime, even in Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But in Germany, you was allowed to requisition anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
